ascend_skill.desc:
When Caroline and Justine are obtained, increase Wonder's skill levels and Thief Tactics by 1 (effective even when Caroline and Justine are not in battle).
Caroline and Justine have 4 sets of Personas, and at the start of battle can select 2 of them. During battle, Caroline and Justine's role is based on the selected combination, and they can receive role effects.
Mask of Mischief and Innocence + Mask of Service and Admonition = Medic
Mask of Mischief and Innocence + Mask of Absurdity and Nonsense = Strategist
Mask of Mischief and Innocence + Mask of Luck and Loss = Sweeper
Mask of Service and Admonition + Mask of Absurdity and Nonsense = Guardian
Mask of Service and Admonition + Mask of Luck and Loss = Saboteur
Mask of Absurdity and Nonsense + Mask of Luck and Loss = Assassin
Skill effects are affected by Desire Level. At the start of battle, gain 25 Desire Level stacks.
ascend_skill.name: Twin Wardens

ascend_skill.desc:
At the start of battle, depending on the selected Personas, gain 2 types of Facade.
At the start or end of Caroline and Justine's turn, if they have 2 types of Facade, automatically activate Two Masks As One on a random target 1 time, prioritizing the target of the previous skill used.
ascend_skill.name: Strict Tolerance

ascend_skill.desc:
When Caroline and Justine gain Facade, gain additional buffs based on the type of Facade.
Facade: Mischief and Innocence = increase party's Attack by 30% for 2 turns.
Facade: Service and Admonition = increase party's damage dealt by 25% for 2 turns.
Facade: Absurdity and Nonsense = Increase critical damage of the Assassin or Sweeper ally with the highest Attack by 20% for 2 turns.
Facade: Luck and Loss = Increase Caroline and Justine's skill damage by 10% for 2 turns.
ascend_skill.name: Callous Kindness

ascend_skill.desc: Increase the skill levels of Selected Skill 1 and Two Masks As One.
ascend_skill.name: Punitive Mercy

ascend_skill.desc: When Caroline and Justine activate their Highlight, for 2 turns, increase their Attack by 40%, damage by 20%, and grant 50% of these effects to other allies.
ascend_skill.name: Execution of Rebirth

ascend_skill.desc: Increase the skill levels of Selected Skill 2 and Thief Tactics.
ascend_skill.name: Humane Prison

ascend_skill.desc:
When this Awareness is unlocked, increase Wonder's skill levels and Thief Tactics by 1 (effective even when Caroline and Justine are not in battle).
At the start of battle, gain 1 True Desire stack. Afterwards, gain 1 True Desire stack every 8 turns.
At the start of Caroline and Justine's turn, spend 1 True Desire stack to strengthen the next activated Two Masks As One.
Buff effect: Spend all Facade stacks when Two Masks As One is activated. Deal damage to the selected target equal to 40% of Attack (8 hits). Increase this skill's effect by 1% for each point of Desire Level. Attributes are Fire, Ice, Electric, Wind, Psychokinesis, Nuclear, Bless, and Curse.
ascend_skill.name: Power to Resist Ruin

highlight_skill.desc:
Based on the 2 Persona sets selected, activate one of the Highlights below (Cooldown times for each Highlight are calculated independently).
Mask of Mischief and Innocence: Increase party's Attack by 24.4%/26.9%/25.9%/28.4% and damage dealt by 34.2%/37.7%/36.3%/39.8% for 2 turns.
Mask of Service and Admonition: Restore party's HP by 43.4%/47.9%/46.1%/50.6% of Caroline and Justine's Attack + 2782/3667/3419/4350.
Increase party's max HP by 9.8%/10.8%/10.4%/11.4% for 2 turns.
Mask of Absurdity and Nonsense: Deal Psy damage to 1 foe equal to 244.0%/269.0%/259.0%/284.0% of Attack, and Nuclear damage equal to 244.0%/269.0%/259.0%/284.0% of Attack (1 hit each).
Increase Attack of Caroline and Justine, and the Assassin or Sweeper with the highest Attack, by 34.2%/37.7%/36.3%/39.8%.
Mask of Luck and Loss: Deal Bless damage to all foes equal to 122.0%/134.5%/129.5%/142.0% of Attack, and deal Curse damage equal to 122.0%/134.5%/129.5%/142.0% (1 hit each).
For 2 turns, increase Caroline and Justine's Attack by 29.3%/32.3%/31.1%/34.1% and critical damage by 19.5%/21.5%/20.7%/22.7%.
highlight_skill.name: Highlight

normal_skill.desc:
Deal Fire damage to 1 foe equal to 74.5%/82.1%/79.0%/86.7% of Attack, and deal Ice damage equal to 74.5%/82.1%/79.0%/86.7% of Attack (1 hit each). Increase this skill's effect by 1% for each point of Desire Level. For 3 turns, increase party's Attack by 39.0%/43.0%/41.4%/45.4% for every 100 points of Desire Level.
Gain 1 Facade: Mischief and Innocence stack.
normal_skill.name: Mask of Mischief and Innocence

normal_skill.desc:
Deal Wind damage to 1 foe equal to 74.5%/82.1%/79.0%/86.7% of Attack, and deal Electric damage equal to 74.5%/82.1%/79.0%/86.7% of Attack (1 hit each). Increase this skill's effect by 1% for each point of Desire Level. For 3 turns, decrease party's damage taken by 9.8%/10.8%/10.4%/11.4% for every 100 points of Desire Level. Also, restore party's HP by 9.8%/10.8%/10.4%/11.4% of Justine and Caroline's Attack + 34.7%/38.3%/36.9%/40.4%.
Gain 1 Facade: Service and Admonition stack.
normal_skill.name: Mask of Service and Admonition

normal_skill.desc:
Deal Psychokinesis damage to 1 foe equal to 74.5%/82.1%/79.0%/86.7% of Attack, and deal Nuclear damage equal to 74.5%/82.1%/79.0%/86.7% of Attack (1 hit each). Increase this skill's effect by 1% for each point of Desire Level. For 3 turns, increase the skill damage of Justine and Caroline, as well as the Assassin or Sweeper ally with the highest Attack, by 4.9%/5.4%/5.2%/5.7% for every 100 points of Desire Level.
Gain 1 Facade: Absurdity and Nonsense stack.
normal_skill.name: Mask of Absurdity and Nonsense

normal_skill.desc:
Deal Bless damage to 1 foe equal to 74.5%/82.1%/79.0%/86.7% of Attack, and Curse damage equal to 74.5%/82.1%/79.0%/86.7% of Attack (1 hit each). Increase this skill's effect by 1% for each point of Desire Level.
For 3 turns, increase Caroline and Justine's Attack by 14.6%/16.1%/15.5%/17.0% + 14.6%/16.1%/15.5%/17.0% for every 100 points of Desire Level, damage dealt by 9.8%/10.8%/10.4%/11.4% + 9.8%/10.8%/10.4%/11.4% for every 100 points of Desire Level, and critical rate by 4.9%/5.4%/5.2%/5.7% + 4.9%/5.4%/5.2%/5.7% for every 100 points of Desire Level.
Gain 1 Facade: Luck and Loss stack.
normal_skill.name: Mask of Luck and Loss

normal_skill.desc:
Usable when any 2 Facade stacks have been gained. Deal Almighty damage to 1 foe equal to 126.9%/139.9%/134.7%/147.7% of Attack. Increase this skill's effect by 1% for each point of Desire Level. Spend all Facade stacks, and based on the combination, activate the following effects.
Facade: Mischief and Innocence + Facade: Service and Admonition = Restore HP to party equal to 52.2%/57.6%/55.4%/60.8% of Attack + 3344/4409/4111/5230. For 2 turns, increase party's damage dealt by 43.9%/48.4%/46.6%/51.1% for every 100 points of Desire Level.
Facade: Mischief and Innocence + Facade: Absurdity and Nonsense = For 2 turns, grant other allies Skill Amplification equal to 14.6%/16.1%/15.5%/17.0%. Also increase other allies' critical damage by 19.5%/21.5%/20.7%/22.7% for every 100 points of Desire Level.
Skill Amplification: Increase the effects of Persona skills and Thief Tactics. This effect is calculated separately from other effects.
Facade: Mischief and Innocence + Facade: Luck and Loss = Change this skill's target to all foes.
Facade: Service and Admonition + Facade: Absurdity and Nonsense = For 2 turns, grant all allies a shield equal to 41.8%/46.1%/44.3%/48.6% of Justine and Caroline's Attack + 2675/3527/3289/4184 and 1 Down Point. Also, increase party's Defense by 48.8%/53.8%/51.8%/56.8% for every 100 points of Desire Level.
Facade: Service and Admonition + Facade: Luck and Loss = Inflict Shocked, Windswept and 2 Curse stacks on the selected target, and gain 2 Blessing stacks. These effects last for 2 turns. Also, for 2 turns, decrease all foes' Defense by 25.4%/28.0%/26.9%/29.5% + 25.4%/28.0%/26.9%/29.5% for each Desire Level stack.
Facade: Absurdity and Nonsense + Facade: Luck and Loss = This skill deals 1 more hit of Almighty damage. For 2 turns, gain Rebel Surveillance.
Rebel Surveillance: When using skills, temporarily increase effects by 4.9%/5.4%/5.2%/5.7% for the Assassin or Sweeper ally with the highest Attack.
normal_skill.name: Two Masks As One

passive_skill.desc:
At the start of battle, increase Desire Level based on Caroline and Justine's base stats.
For every 100 points of their Attack, increase Desire Level by 1 (up to 45).
For every 2% of their damage bonus, increase Desire Level by 1 (up to 15).
For every 10% of their critical damage, increase Desire Level by 1 (up to 15).
passive_skill.name: Overseer of Rehabilitation

passive_skill.desc:
Gain stat bonuses based on skill combinations.
Mask of Mischief and Innocence + Mask of Service and Admonition = Increase healing by 21.0%. When on the field, increase party's Attack by 24.0%.
Mask of Mask of Mischief and Innocence + Mask of Absurdity and Nonsense = Increase Speed by 5. When on the field, increase party's Attack by 30.0%.
Mask of Mischief and Innocence + Mask of Luck and Loss = Increase critical rate by 15.0%.
Mask of Mask of Service and Admonition + Mask of Absurdity and Nonsense = Increase own shield effect by 21.0%.
Mask of Service and Admonition + Mask of Luck and Loss = Increase Speed by 5. When on the field, increase party's damage taken by 24.0%.
Mask of Absurdity and Nonsense + Mask of Luck and Loss = Increase critical damage by 30.0%.
passive_skill.name: Oxymoron
